name: BabySkullz
description:
BabySkullz are the first inhabitants of Skullz City — a place where life
is peaceful and neighbors are friendly — They take things slow, have a
positive energy, a blessed soul, believe that the future is full of
surprises and that it holdz more than meets the eye. We call them
Believerz because they trusted us in rocking their world before anyone
else.
